	<LINE>PRISON GATE MISSION.</LINE>
	<LINE>23 William Street, Calton.</LINE>
	<LINE>This institution is for the purpose of providing</LINE>
	<LINE>employment for discharged female prisoners who are</LINE>
	<LINE>desirous of doing better. The women are employed</LINE>
	<LINE>in washing and laundry work, sewing, and knitting,</LINE>
	<LINE>for which they are paid a small daily wage and their</LINE>
	<LINE>food. Average number of inmates 53, of whom</LINE>
	<LINE>about 20 lodge in the Home.</LINE>
